data.description: This home is a fantastic option for those looking for a classic, traditional home with plenty of space! This home boasts five bedrooms, two bathrooms, 2 car garage, and an above ground pool. As you walk up to the home, you'll notice the classic brick exterior and traditional architecture, giving it a timeless feel. The interior is spacious & inviting, with 12 foot ceilings in living area and plenty of space for entertaining guests or family. The five bedrooms are perfect for a large family or for those who need extra space for guests or a home office. The master bedroom is the perfect place to relax after a long day with wood floors, an ensuite bath with a garden tub & separate shower. Large cabinet-desk in formal dining conveys with the home. The above ground pool is the perfect place to cool off in hot Texas afternoons, and the backyard deck provides plenty of space for BBQs. Located in the beautiful city of Mesquite, which offers plenty of shopping, dining, & entertainment options.
